
* Data
The study uses data on S&P500 retrieved from "https://www.slickcharts.com/sp500" which includes S&P constituents over period from X to Y.

Data on /*market return and*/ risk free rate comes from Kennet French data library.

Data on daily stock prices is obtained from CCM data from the WRDS database for the time period between Nov 1st 2019 and Dec 31st 2020. This is to ensure that for each firm we have a year of data prior to the event examined by this study.

Data on S&P index daily return comes from the WRDS database.

